HOUSTON, United States of America, January 31, 2019/APO Group/ --
                                                        
                            National Energy Services Reunited Corp. (''NESR'') (NASDAQ: NESR) (NASDAQ: NESRW) (NESR.com), a national, industry-leading provider of integrated energy services in the Middle East and North Africa (''MENA'') region, today announced that it will report results for the fourth quarter and full year 2018 on Monday, February 25, 2019. A conference call is scheduled for 9:00 AM ET on February 25, 2019.



Investors, analysts and members of the media interested in listening to the call are encouraged to participate by dialing into the toll-free line at 1-877-407-0312 or the international line at 1-201-389-0899. A live, listen-only webcast will also be available in the investors section ofÂ www.NESR.com. A replay of the conference call will be available a few hours after the event in the investors section of the Company's website.